  "texts": [
    "In general, we found that our model performs well across datasets with a variety of tasks in both older and younger populations.",
    "The amount of predicted internal content is highly correlated with actual internal detail counts in narratives.",
    "Likewise, the amount of predicted external content is highly correlated with actual external detail counts.",
    "Importantly, in most of the datasets content misclassification is relatively low: the number of internal details has little relationship to the amount of predicted external content.",
    "Likewise, there is no strong relationship between the number of external details and predicted internal content."
  ],
